WEBVTT

00:00.038 --> 00:01.968
Previously on
<i>"Legends of Tomorrow"...</i>

00:01.971 --> 00:03.278
You and I dating would be
totally weird.

00:03.279 --> 00:04.272
Totally weird.

00:04.278 --> 00:06.298
Hank is running
some secret project.

00:06.310 --> 00:08.810
A man came to me, Neron.
He offered me a deal.

00:08.890 --> 00:11.060
Don't tell me you're having
second thoughts.

00:11.070 --> 00:12.440
I have a new partner now.
My son.

00:12.520 --> 00:15.490
- I don't need you anymore.
- I don't need you anymore, either.

00:15.570 --> 00:17.990
- Dad?
- I'm sorry.

00:19.190 --> 00:20.700
I didn't kill Nate's dad.

00:20.770 --> 00:22.870
Sara, you're asking me
to risk everything

00:22.940 --> 00:25.200
for some conspiracy theory?
For a bunch of monsters?

00:25.280 --> 00:27.000
- Ava, don't do this.
- I'm done.

00:27.010 --> 00:29.000
<i>Ava and I didn't just
get into an argument.</i>

00:29.070 --> 00:30.840
<i>She asked me to leave.</i>

00:36.120 --> 00:38.550
Come on, Ava, open up.

00:41.210 --> 00:45.260
Look, I... I miss you.

00:45.270 --> 00:47.850
And I'm sorry things went down
the way they did,

00:47.930 --> 00:50.520
but please just open the door.

00:52.360 --> 00:54.690
<i>Well, technically
this is still our apartment.</i>

